2009 IN BOND & FINANCIAL PRODUCTS, BUSINESS RETENTION RATES REMAINED STRONG BUT DECREASED FROM 2008, PRIMARILY IN PROFESSIONAL LIABILITY. RENEWAL PREMIUM CHANGES IN 2009

