A UNIVERSAL SHELF REGISTRATION STATEMENT FOR THE POTENTIAL OFFERING AND SALE OF SECURITIES. THE COMPANY MAY OFFER THESE SECURITIES FROM TIME TO TIME AT PRICES AND ON OTHER TERMS TO BE DETERMINED AT

THE TIME OF OFFERING. DURING 2010 AND 2009, THE COMPANY ISSUED SECURITIES WITH A PRINCIPAL AMOUNT OF $1.25 BILLION AND $500 MILLION, RESPECTIVELY, UNDER THE SHELF REGISTRATION STATEMENT.

