CONTAINING EMBEDDED CONVERSION OPTIONS THAT ARE VALUED SEPARATELY FROM THE HOST BOND CONTRACT IN THE AMOUNT DISCLOSED IN LEVEL 2FIXED MATURITIES. AT DECEMBER 31, 2009, THE

COMPANY HELD NON-PUBLIC STOCK WARRANTS IN A PUBLIC COMPANY FOR WHICH IT ESTIMATED FAIR VALUE USING AN

