APRIL 1, 2004, THE TRAVELERS COMPANIES, INC. FULLY AND UNCONDITIONALLY GUARANTEED THE PAYMENT OF ALL PRINCIPAL, PREMIUMS, IF ANY, AND INTEREST ON CERTAIN DEBT

