THE COMPANY'S OTHER POSTRETIREMENT BENEFIT PLAN HAD FINANCIAL ASSETS OF $20 MILLION AT DECEMBER 31, 2010 AND 2009, WHICH

ARE MEASURED AT FAIR VALUE ON A RECURRING BASIS. THE ASSETS ARE

